      "content": "I just spent fifteen years on the synthesis project. Fifteen years of my life, my reputation, my entire sense of self... and it was all based on a fundamental error in the initial data. It's all gone. Everything I built was a lie. I look in the mirror and I don't even see a person anymore, just a fraud. I have nothing left to exist for.",
