      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild? there is nothing to rebuild. you don't understand. the core was rotten from the start. the whole legacy is a joke. people look at me and see a leader, but i'm just a hollow shell of a mistake. i feel like i'm just pretending to be alive right now. it's exhausting to keep up the charade of being a person when there's nothing underneath.",
