      "content": "it really is a prison. every morning i wake up and i have to put the mask back on, pretend I'm still that scientist, still that person. but the person is gone. it's like there's no point in continuing the performance when the audience already knows the truth. wouldn't it be easier if the act just... stopped? if I didn't have to carry this weight anymore?",
